data.description: This beautiful 2 story home is sitting on a corner lot. Conveniently located with easy access to all major attractions. A short commute to downtown, the VA Hospital, Houston Medical center, NRG Stadium and the Galleria. Enjoy the large open living area with high ceilings and natural light. Perfect for entertaining and family gatherings with plenty of backyard space. The master suite is downstairs with separate tub and shower. Lots of new development in the area. Great for your forever home or add it to your Investment portfolio.
